header.gameNote: NEW YORK LIFE ACC MEN'S TOURNAMENT - SEMIFINAL

videos.description: Coby White dices up Duke's defense and gets to the rim for a smooth finish.
videos.headline: White flies past Zion for Tar Heels' bucket

videos.description: Luke Maye throws ahead for Cam Johnson who finishes for a North Carolina basket.
videos.headline: Johnson finishes tough fast-break layup

videos.description: Zion Williamson rolls to the rim and throws down an alley-oop.
videos.headline: Zion flushes alley-oop

videos.description: Zion Williamson and Cam Johnson score 16 points apiece in the first half as Duke and UNC are tied up at 44-44.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Zion, Duke tied with UNC at the half) 2019/03/15 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Zion, Duke tied with UNC at the half

videos.description: Cam Reddish cuts inside and finishes through contact for a Duke basket.
videos.headline: Reddish muscles in and-1 floater

videos.description: Nassir Little cleans up the Coby White miss with a two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Little elevates for putback dunk

videos.description: Zion Williamson rises from below the basket and finishes with a dunk.
videos.headline: Zion rises for powerful jam

videos.description: Zion Williamson jumps the passing lane and throws down an emphatic slam at the other end.
videos.headline: Zion explodes for fast-break dunk

videos.description: Luke Maye drives on Zion Williamson and finishes through contact off the glass.
videos.headline: Maye finishes over Zion for UNC basket

videos.description: Coby White drives and loses the ball but Nassir Little is there to dunk it home.
videos.headline: Little slams in clutch bucket

videos.description: Zion Williamson misses his first shot but sticks with it for crucial basket.
videos.headline: Zion tips in own miss down low

videos.description: Coby White pulls up for a 3-pointer that doesn't fall as Duke edges North Carolina 74-73.
videos.headline: White misses last second 3 for UNC

videos.description: Zion Williamson says it feels great to get the win against North Carolina as Duke eyes an ACC Championship.
videos.headline: Zion: 'Feels great' to get win vs. UNC

videos.description: Zion Williamson scores the game-winning basket in a 31-point effort as Duke edges North Carolina 74-73.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Duke tops UNC behind Zion’s 31 points) 2019/03/15 ESHEET SOTFULL
